        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Methane Super-Emitter Strategy Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to enter an agreement with the National Academies of Sciences, Engineering, and Medicine to develop a science-based strategy to assess, evaluate, and make recommendations regarding the use of present and future greenhouse gas monitoring and detection capabilities.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
